23:24.960 --> 23:39.980
<b>Episode 3: "Guardians of the Crimson Demon Village"</b>

23:25.310 --> 23:26.720
Big trouble, Megumin!

23:26.720 --> 23:30.220
That alum, Bukkorori, is being weird 
and asking for romantic advice!

23:30.220 --> 23:33.150
Wow, a completely worthless NEET putting 
his creepiness on full display!

23:33.150 --> 23:34.580
That's harsh! Isn't he 
like your big brother?

23:34.580 --> 23:36.480
I've never once considered 
that thing to be my brother.

23:36.480 --> 23:39.040
So mean! N-Next time, 
we'll be at your school with an...

23:39.040 --> 23:41.040
Explosion!
